  <div id="aboutus" class="span4 red_title">
    <h3>About WeTheNation</h3>
    <p>WeTheNation is a non-partisan, not for profit, application that provides the facts about Congress including its current members and current legislation. WeTheNation provides users with a way to keep track of, vote on, and share their opinions on current members and bills in Congress. WeTheNation is your starting point for getting involved in politics and the issues important to you.</p>
    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>Our mission is simple; to make politics more engaging, interesting, and understandable. We know how difficult it can be to stay up to date on bills and members in the news and we hope to provide our users with a portal of information that is both factual and easily accessible. Knowledge is power and we want to empower all citizens to be as educated on the issues as possible. Real change starts at the Congressional level, and its starts with you.</p>
  </div>
